[Measles immunization was initiated in Myanmar during 1987, with the 1st dose targeting children under 9 months http://www.searo.who.int/myanmar/areas/immunization_measlescampaign/en/. Although measles infection mainly affects young children, the people who were born before 1987 or who opted out prior to the full implementation of the immunization program are susceptible to the infection as well. - Mod.YMA

